{"tid":427863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔連自己人都唔撐，仲學咩人講獨立","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T05:34:04.000Z","uid":1627,"like":75,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e21d667bed8631dc0c0e2313a1775add4ffff861","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"一方面又話要排擠支那人，建立香港民族，另一方面又不斷踩自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連團結都做唔到仲話要獨立，笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪講句，其他國家既人都比香港人更珍惜香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431f6107f129150606a93dbb9d2a1ccdb7f43843","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"鍵盤鍵國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cdd2fc088d36fae0632044f95c6e3d3d8ec99d","tid":427863,"uid":102700,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"香港人冇根呢個concept<br />\n個個都只係想係度搵夠錢之後移民"},{"pid":"efa420ebc468dbff5843849b84e67f51daee70a3","tid":427863,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95feb10d40680508c68358a1efbcf8302c34b278","tid":427863,"uid":29270,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"踩自已人唔緊要，有理據咪踩囉<br />\n<br />\n體育台都話有精彩辯駁睇<br />\n時事台反曹星如批人，個個用個人感覺就當真，拳例都唔識多條<br />\n<br />\n仲既態度點樣反政府暴政，一比人問起就發現原來冇理據冇論點<br />\n<br />\n得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9dc496546463b41fefe71a696da75405cea4a3","tid":427863,"uid":810,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"總知咩都拉去講港獨就岩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26657fab32a280d65fb8f5f476e821c40ee2969","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩自已人唔緊要，有理據咪踩囉<br />\n<br />\n體育台都話有精彩辯駁睇<br />\n時事台反曹星如批人，個個用個人感覺就當真，拳例都唔識多條<br />\n<br />\n仲既態度點樣反政府暴政，一比人問起就發現原來冇理據冇論點<br />\n<br />\n得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本唔抵得人地成功，你話第二個國家既人都話，但連自己人都眼紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔呢種思想真係好奇怪"},{"pid":"0650cd87d4e0828ce7861fe4da20a17ddb8a4c35","tid":427863,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩自已人唔緊要，有理據咪踩囉<br />\n<br />\n體育台都話有精彩辯駁睇<br />\n時事台反曹星如批人，個個用個人感覺就當真，拳例都唔識多條<br />\n<br />\n仲既態度點樣反政府暴政，一比人問起就發現原來冇理據冇論點<br />\n<br />\n得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地個態度係人多聲大夾惡就係道理"},{"pid":"eaf6f41ac361c8a0079ca447b47d03b0a5080141","tid":427863,"uid":62494,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:33:24.000Z","msg":"啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象"},{"pid":"3af3bf37b8de0c4dfcb0e1b2cc25388533e6dd34","tid":427863,"uid":71647,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"未見過傅家俊 李慧詩有人踩<br />\n因為大家都知佢地先係世界級<br />\n星仔就....."},{"pid":"5dc3f49a27ed073d2758c09ec473cf386b94ffcb","tid":427863,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"強力部門唔想香港人成日講香港精神"},{"pid":"4d32fd3ead4ca7005fcbab79c970eeee32719476","tid":427863,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象</blockquote><br />\n諗到要同你呢d撚屌一齊搞港獨就覺得自己天真"},{"pid":"8638edb4acfa7f2e1fc07ff92f1782640ffb5a4b","tid":427863,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象</blockquote><br />\n緊係啦，根本香港人，最起碼連登仔就唔當拳擊係一回事<br />\n<br />\n其它運動就叫識下例<br />\n<br />\n係去到拳擊個個當爛仔交睇<br />\n單係時事台，已經一堆post話「曹星如睇落比較傷應當輸」<br />\n大佬呀人地有拳例、有規則架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e915d47d0628a535c5d6695647fbf38b12fa6","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總知咩都拉去講港獨就岩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCC台唔講港獨不如講台獨啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8681d6de281b0acf3eeca83fd9cb857b20bd78a5","tid":427863,"uid":5600,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"勝之不武咪反囉<br />\n香港人身份大撚晒? 點都要撐<br />\n<br />\n有冇人反傅家俊,有冇人反李惠詩?"},{"pid":"082e1cb865b002b5c4a9637fd42f8e71cf90dc64","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勝之不武咪反囉<br />\n香港人身份大撚晒? 點都要撐<br />\n<br />\n有冇人反傅家俊,有冇人反李惠詩?</blockquote><br />\n連登仔仲專業過日本裁判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9ee18d65f7757eebd659284832ffae11fe3795","tid":427863,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"話「有冇人反其它運動員」果批<br />\n<br />\n好心問下自已你地當拳擊係乜先啦<br />\n<br />\n甚少有人唔識足球球例，就去挑戰裁判同賽果<br />\n係去到拳擊，就一堆拳擊專家彈晒出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223e8c7a35a9081ec2ed6ec5740dc197c810f85d","tid":427863,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg&h=f815dfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg&h=72370655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a63202061051cc8da7fef9408ebff7ae032095","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg&h=f815dfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg&h=72370655&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以？你就選擇性無視我其他post？<br />\n你都係想話我係支那五毛啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有五毛話支那係支那呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb5daf255da0344642fb790d9f61c9f02636cb6","tid":427863,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"你唔批鬥個班去日本既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37800c013842de738ba7d70c28c323eec5de7ad9","tid":427863,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"咁都拉去支持港獨嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔俾係港豬講嘅"},{"pid":"88cd78b5dff5127f98860e775d296cd1adcb7bf6","tid":427863,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點"},{"pid":"b616dca90d33c775803d9c03b94ea7af5aa09f49","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71339fb39a3a3d241cb3072c6c58e4ea42cb5b2e","tid":427863,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇過2002世界盃?裁判?"},{"pid":"5c3db120a877972a61d0139167d0d72f15d651c1","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇過2002世界盃?裁判?</blockquote><br />\n你本身有既定立場咁冇野好講啦"},{"pid":"eee369a108e7832eff89d4414f3e3b6b16f148a6","tid":427863,"uid":151421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇過2002世界盃?裁判?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泡菜真係。。。還掂佢都黑，黑多兩場咪捧盃。"},{"pid":"fea79210468ff81947ab19b5d7c8f4bfc5cd6f49","tid":427863,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇過2002世界盃?裁判?</blockquote><br />\n你本身有既定立場咁冇野好講啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係咩既唔既得立場問題,我同屋企人睇足成粒鐘好明顯係河野D擊中次數多好多,計點數都應該河野贏九條街"},{"pid":"8f286469222dd76f4ae018372eaff20753f4946d","tid":427863,"uid":476,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話「有冇人反其它運動員」果批<br />\n<br />\n好心問下自已你地當拳擊係乜先啦<br />\n<br />\n甚少有人唔識足球球例，就去挑戰裁判同賽果<br />\n係去到拳擊，就一堆拳擊專家彈晒出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得太多唔識突然拳友走去扮專家🤔<br />\n<br />\n以前大家唔識波都有共識講少句齋睇 而家唔知咩事"},{"pid":"168f1fd4759660d02c723defd11b87f600634479","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鳩撐咩屌你老母<br />\n理性宏觀世界觀先係香港呢個地方優點</blockquote><br />\n賽果贏連登仔話唔服，連裁判都判合理連登仔又話黑哨，呢D叫理性？偏見就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇過2002世界盃?裁判?</blockquote><br />\n你本身有既定立場咁冇野好講啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係咩既唔既得立場問題,我同屋企人睇足成粒鐘好明顯係河野D擊中次數多好多,計點數都應該河野贏九條街</blockquote><br />\n你係真係專業既真正評點數嗰個就會係你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cb699f7b8989a35433d9f98650d3d20da6541b","tid":427863,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總知咩都拉去講港獨就岩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩 乜能都係關港獨<br />\n年青一代 令我睇到光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227e0fd5b4e9dee7af350d0be883b54552695017","tid":427863,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"一定係因為佔中"},{"pid":"0b2aecf1b4bd1b6655aa5593d54cd781bcff37ab","tid":427863,"uid":125111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"其實好多人唔係屌阿Rex<br />\n係屌撚緊個制度同拳例<br />\n<br />\n如果因為自己人就要撐<br />\n同班盲撐盲反又有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n阿Rex有努力大家都認同<br />\n但利用呢個制度下走正面<br />\n同玩「法律罅」有乜分別<br />\n贏得合理 但不能服眾<br />\n<br />\n咪就係一班「富人政權」所為咩?<br />\n要獨立/ 要民主都好啦<br />\n我地一路都屌緊個制度<br />\n如果制度不公都要撐要維護所衍生的事<br />\n<br />\n你先係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一句到尾: 今次害尻左Rex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0e6193cf6f86af4004fdfa3b2694a195e493a4","tid":427863,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg&h=f815dfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg&h=72370655&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以？你就選擇性無視我其他post？<br />\n你都係想話我係支那五毛啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有五毛話支那係支那呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲熱狗屌到行添，so what?<br />\n閣下言論：要改變人'唔好做奴隸'既睇法，<br />\n但又唔好屌中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又'不如安份做港豬'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011921_98c91cb0ea461632f17dd12d99d41efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011921_98c91cb0ea461632f17dd12d99d41efe.jpg&h=5a42ac10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011954_0b5507e34dec89b6e93ca0c13efc938f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011954_0b5507e34dec89b6e93ca0c13efc938f.jpg&h=154c07da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011922_6eb4db96f7fe63788a5a896f2ec0105c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011922_6eb4db96f7fe63788a5a896f2ec0105c.jpg&h=262d9c90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33885027b9b7baa17b5f69e91f2a0367ecde7481","tid":427863,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"強力部門唔想香港人成日講香港精神，明唔明"},{"pid":"82823150506dbf2b3889f68222c261968d513577","tid":427863,"uid":127716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:48:45.000Z","msg":"五毛出黎抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3079e158328b1a79d966f5d6168878d7d0b6bf3c","tid":427863,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:57:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oct5近期活躍五毛<br />\nJR<br />\n三色貓<br />\n民國復興<br />\n熱血藍絲<br />\nbb chu<br />\nRedbaron<br />\n阿古路<br />\nnewlife<br />\n優美開始<br />\n人見人愛<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0a9ada161348e8a12d8a73573e174c84204aac1f","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_b08c40f7af49553d43f2585702d56b49.jpg&h=f815dfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F004107_ff68044076d7c76ef1ad7c63fdf288af.jpg&h=72370655&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以？你就選擇性無視我其他post？<br />\n你都係想話我係支那五毛啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有五毛話支那係支那呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲熱狗屌到行添，so what?<br />\n閣下言論：要改變人'唔好做奴隸'既睇法，<br />\n但又唔好屌中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又'不如安份做港豬'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011921_98c91cb0ea461632f17dd12d99d41efe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011921_98c91cb0ea461632f17dd12d99d41efe.jpg&h=5a42ac10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011954_0b5507e34dec89b6e93ca0c13efc938f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011954_0b5507e34dec89b6e93ca0c13efc938f.jpg&h=154c07da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/011922_6eb4db96f7fe63788a5a896f2ec0105c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F011922_6eb4db96f7fe63788a5a896f2ec0105c.jpg&h=262d9c90&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係連登屌中共有撚用？<br />\n獨派而家俾人既印象就係冇乜實質行動，剩係得把口，你地仲要加深人地對你既壞印象？咩道理呀？同你唔同意見就係五毛？我好撚驚呀，我係咁話中國係支那會唔會冇錢收架？<br />\n同埋我句不如香港人安分做港豬既前提下係香港人真係唔想要民主，呢個唔係而家廢中廢老既意願咩？斷章取義到咁？<br />\n仲有，陳雲熱狗係主僕關係咩？呢個比喻唔多掂喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8aa00ae2d0c24118318746dfa735605ff1ce289","tid":427863,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"平時講句野唔啱聽又話你五毛又起你底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登講團結，收皮啦"},{"pid":"6a4cec534cfff57507444f3539bad9cf4dc1c12d","tid":427863,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7b6fd9aa01fe180ef950edd1a5fe123439f3433","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時講句野唔啱聽又話你五毛又起你底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登講團結，收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n乜都俾人話五毛，我好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fd360ee47e43830a1957d3c75a5f8a5e79b828","tid":427863,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"俾你獨立到，第二日又批鬥個總統啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fb8eecf2bc0959e939913c69de43ac68f27888","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾你獨立到，第二日又<span style=\"color: red;\">上連登</span>批鬥個總統啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7bda200db13bc19f0866cfccc4cf1a382b97fda3","tid":427863,"uid":37443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"同意 睇下人地國家隊插水會唔會俾自己既球迷笑"},{"pid":"af694ee88594d4c230b6d9db37d354f0adda1b51","tid":427863,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"內鬥基因<br />\n中國人係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"87b87e63ab4ab8153159893567124bbc1a840cc3","tid":427863,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多人唔係屌阿Rex<br />\n係屌撚緊個制度同拳例<br />\n<br />\n如果因為自己人就要撐<br />\n同班盲撐盲反又有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n阿Rex有努力大家都認同<br />\n但利用呢個制度下走正面<br />\n同玩「法律罅」有乜分別<br />\n贏得合理 但不能服眾<br />\n<br />\n咪就係一班「富人政權」所為咩?<br />\n要獨立/ 要民主都好啦<br />\n我地一路都屌緊個制度<br />\n如果制度不公都要撐要維護所衍生的事<br />\n<br />\n你先係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一句到尾: 今次害尻左Rex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家都係打拳例<br />\n唔係打到對方爆缸<br />\n想ko對手做唔到輸分<br />\n咪策略失算<br />\n體育唔同打交<br />\n要ko先叫羸就唔好睇boxing<br />\n例本身係公平<br />\n<br />\n武術同體育係兩回事啱架<br />\n亦唔係第一日講<br />\n只係好多連仔以為發現新大陸ja"},{"pid":"52a4b03ba7c7e8a550c144102055f64a1c442441","tid":427863,"uid":69754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象</blockquote><br />\n巴打講得岩<br />\n有無人駁到？<br />\n如果一個洗分商業味極重既運動運動員代表到香港<br />\n支持果班人反而更應該檢討一下<br />\n明明有一班本土運動員更值得我地關注<br />\n你有無支持？"},{"pid":"fd4875200caed925e07bfb86c8575ee1263b0952","tid":427863,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"一向都係鍵盤建國，你咁認真做乜？<br />\n<br />\n排支那？你睇越黎越多人用淘寶，順豐收貨條隊d 客全部係後生仔多<br />\n<br />\n連登仔口中既廢老藍絲反而唔講淘寶囉"},{"pid":"8ff93eea47799c0e166293a5a66dc31d71682dc0","tid":427863,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象</blockquote><br />\n巴打講得岩<br />\n有無人駁到？<br />\n如果一個洗分商業味極重既運動運動員代表到香港<br />\n支持果班人反而更應該檢討一下<br />\n明明有一班本土運動員更值得我地關注<br />\n你有無支持？</blockquote><br />\n商業就唔抵撐<br />\n呢個咪港酸logic囉<br />\n睇下世界球會球星<br />\n幾多神級運動員同商業掛勾"},{"pid":"4fe75493bdd0532017d998c7fc117956e48aabb3","tid":427863,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"自己人就要撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e8ff4aebc744baa13f2bb13e704f2b2efa0a6b","tid":427863,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱既就撐,楊文蔚 歐鎧淳 傅家俊 李麗珊呢D邊有反?<br />\n係呢條撚屌曹星如又刷數據又黑哨咁叫人點撐得落?撐佢盞更加損害香港形象</blockquote><br />\n巴打講得岩<br />\n有無人駁到？<br />\n如果一個洗分商業味極重既運動運動員代表到香港<br />\n支持果班人反而更應該檢討一下<br />\n明明有一班本土運動員更值得我地關注<br />\n你有無支持？</blockquote><br />\n商業就唔抵撐<br />\n呢個咪港酸logic囉<br />\n睇下世界球會球星<br />\n幾多神級運動員同商業掛勾</blockquote><br />\n連登仔logic：商業=有錢賺=黑哨"}]}